data.description: Priced To Sell!!, 3 bed 1.5 bath home, new hurricane impact windows, new roof, new AC, new washer, and dryer, hard surface throughout, one car garage. Completely fenced in large backyard, above ground pool to cool off on hot summer days, quiet neighborhood. Close to schools, medical, shopping, dining, all things Port Charlotte.   Snowbirds you will love this location, no flood zone, home is solid.
